text: Most Expensivest is a television series on Viceland hosted by 2 Chainz. It premiered on November 15, 2017. The show was renewed for a third season on May 7, 2019. ==Series overview== The series delves into the most expensive items such as food, drinks, and even jewelry. ==References == Category:Viceland original programming Category:2 Chainz Category:2017 American television series debuts
title: Most Expensivest
